            +b the mitigation works as designed and"
        requirement_id "IEC 62443-4-1:2018 SVV-2 a"
        title "Threat Mitigation Testing - Plan Creation and Execution"
        description "This requirement focuses on the creation and execution of plans to ensure that
            +b each mitigation implemented to address a specific threat has been adequately
