                    +b assessments."
        [ related_standards
            {
                standard "ISO/IEC 27034-1:2011"
                reference "This standard focuses on the application security framework and includes
                    +b elements related to secure design and threat mitigation, which are relevant to
                    +b developing test plans for threat mitigations."
            {
                standard "NIST SP 800-53 Rev. 5"
                reference "The NIST Special Publication provides guidelines for security and privacy
