                    +b with the need for thorough threat mitigation testing."
            {
                standard "ISO/IEC 15408-3:2008"
                reference "Common Criteria for Information Technology Security Evaluation, Part 3, which
                    +b includes security assurance requirements that cover testing and evaluation of
                    +b security functions, relevant for verifying threat mitigations."